content.rendered:
Directed by Venu Sriram

Written by Shoojit Sircar. Aniruddha Roy Chowdhury. Ritesh Shah. Venu Sriram. Mamidala Thirupathi. Venu Sriram

Cast Pawan Kalyan(Satyadev Konidela). Nivetha Thomas(Pallavi Vemula). Anjali(Zareena Begum). Ananya Nagalla(Divya Nayak). Prakash Raj(Nanda Gopal). Shruti Haasan(Satyadev’s wife). Vamsi Krishna(Vamshi). Mukesh Rishi(MP Korentla Rajendar). Srikanth Iyengar(CI Yugandhar). Lirisha(SI Saraladevi). Kedar Shankar(Pallavi’s father). Kamal Kamaraju(Anwar). Chakrapani Ananda(Divya’s father). Anish Kuruvilla(Zareena’s manager). Subhalekha Sudhakar(Flat owner). Sarath Babu(Discipline Committee chairman). Chaitanya Krishna(Satyadev’s friend). Shivakumar Ramachandravarapu(Vishwa). Nagineedu(ACP Ravinder). Sayaji Shinde(Minister Siva Reddy). Dev Gill(Satyadev’s enemy).C.V.L. Narasimha Rao. Darbha Appaji Ambarisha(Shruthi Haasan father).Ashok.Ram Babu. Syed Abid Bhushan(Key role).Bhushanam.Chaitanya.Hari Chandra.Devi.Dhanalakshmi. Sammeta Gandhi(Ranganna).Guruswamy. Kalyan(Banti).Railway Ravi Kiran.Krishna.Gongul Krishna.Roopa Lakshmi.Chandramogli Madem.Naga Mahesh.Sunitha Manohar.Meer.Murthy.Padma.Parthasarathy.Siva Parvathi.Pragnya.Rajini.Prameela Rani.Govind Rao.Kameshwara Rao.Krishneswara Rao.Jyothi Reddy. Ramesh Reddy(Chari).Surender Reddy.Viswender Reddy.Satya.Rajendar Satyajith.Lab Sharath. Amit Sharma(Shiva).Railway Srinivas.Vadlamani Srinivas.Subbaraju.Suma.Surya. Swarnakanth(Asst.Lawyer to Nanda gopal).Valli.Temper Vamsi.Venugopal. Subba Rao Vepada((as Kancharapalem Raju))

Language Telugu

Producers Harish Pai. Dil Raju. Harshith Reddy. Sireesh. Sk. Zabeer.

Production Sri Venkateswara Creations. Bayview Projects
